\subsection{Frobenius matrix}
\begin{definition}\label{modlgal.frobenius_matrix}
\uses{modlgal,modlgal.absolute_frobenius}
A **Frobenius matrix** for a {{KNOWL('modlgal','mod-$\ell$ Galois representation')}}  is an element of the conjugacy class of the image of the {{KNOWL('modlgal.absolute_frobenius','absolute Frobenius')}} element associated to a particular prime.

\end{definition}


